citations.desc: ACCESS AND INSPECTION OF RECORDS AND PROPERTY; SUBMISSION OF ITINERARIES.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 10 am on
04/02/2015. APHIS inspector made contact with Licensee via cell phone. Licensee was away and unable to come
home until the afternoon.
Additional Inspectors
Lundy Kendall, Animal Care Inspector
